RaidSkill.Name: Color's Echo - Alpha
RaidSkill.Desc: Shiroko*Terror and Phrenapates simulataneously use their skills. Shiroko*Terror: Deals 2500% damage to enemies in a straight line. Phrenapates: Deals 6000% damage to enemies in a circular area. During this skill, CC effects inflicted will fill Phrenapates' circular CC gauge proportional to the duration of the effect. When the gauge reaches an amount equivalent to 4.5s, interrupts Phrenapates skill and increases the of all enemies by 100% for 17s.

RaidSkill.Name: Atra-Hasis' Ark Defense System
RaidSkill.Desc: Phrenapates uses all the energy of the Atra-Hasis' Ark to fire at the enemy, dealing damage to all enemies equal to 1000% of their Max HP.
